\par \'c7\'fcnk\'fc ya\'feam, organizmay\'fd olu\'feturan par\'e7alar\'fdn ya da molek\'fcllerin birarada bulunmas\'fdndan \'e7ok daha \'f6te, metafizik bir kavramd\'fdr. Ya\'feam, Allah'\'fdn "Hayy" (Hayat sahibi) s\'fdfat\'fdn\'fdn bir yans\'fdmas\'fdd\'fd
