\par }{\f0\fs22\lang1031\langfe1055\langnp1031\insrsid15231856 Evr}{\f100\fs22\lang1031\langfe1055\langnp1031\insrsid15231856 im, canl\'fdl\'fdk i\'e7in gerekli malzemenin olu\'femas\'fdn\'fd da, bir araya geli\'feini de a\'e7\'fdklayamamaktad\'fdr; tabii canl
